### Check if email was sent (look at Mailtrap inbox)
### Then copy the verification token from the email URL and use it below

### Verify Email
POST http://localhost:4001/customer-auth/verify-email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "PASTE_TOKEN_FROM_EMAIL_HERE"
}

### Try to Login (should fail before verification)
